#FeminaCelebs: Janhvi Kapoor steps into a new role as Friend of the Maison for Baume & Mercier, alongside the launch of its Joia collection. Rooted in individuality and instinctive elegance, the partnership reflects a shared take on modern femininity—one that feels personal, fluid, and self-defined.
With her evolving on-screen presence and understated confidence, Kapoor mirrors the spirit of the collection, where style is less about perfection and more about authenticity. At its core, the collaboration signals a shift toward celebrating women as they are—complex, expressive, and entirely their own.
